HEADWORD: Moonblink
<hw>Moon"blink`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A temporary
blindness, or impairment of sight, said to be caused by sleeping in the
moonlight; -- sometimes called <altname>nyctalopia</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mooncalf</ent>⟦br⟧
